	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">INSIDE MUSEUM CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Walk around:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Choose game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Press and hold to speed up movement when walking forward or backward:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Return to normal forward position:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Look up:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Sidestep to the left or right:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 or R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select games / Select menu:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">THE GENJI AND THE HEIKE CLANS CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move, strike from overhead, duck:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Jump:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Downward strike with sword:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open options window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enter credits:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Start game / Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">PAC-LAND CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Jump or select trip number:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move character left, rapidly to increase speed, hold down to maintain fast speed:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Move character right, rapidly to increase speed, hold down to maintain fast speed:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Open options window:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enter credits:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Start game / Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ASSAULT CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Control the left tank tread:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Control right tank tread:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X, Circle, Square or Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire / Shoot normal shots:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1, L2, R1 or R2 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enter credits:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Start game / Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ORDYNE CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move character:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Fire / Shoot main weapon:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Circle or Square Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Drop bombs:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R2 or X Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enter credits:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Start game / Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br>
			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">THE RETURN OF ISHTAR CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Move KI in one of eight directions:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Moves Gil in one of eight directions:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;X, Circle, Square or Triangle Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Cast a spell:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;L1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Select an incarnation/spell with the directional buttons; press directional buttons up, down, left or right to make selection:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;R1 Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Enter credits:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Select Button</font>
                  <br>&nbsp; Start game / Pause game:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;Start Button</font><br><br>
